int x;
int y;
x = 10;
y = 20;

if (x) {
    return y;
}

while (x) {
    x = 0;
}

for (int i; i; i) {
    do {
        return 1;
    }
}

Keyword: int, char, if, else, while, for, do, return
Identifiers: Sequence initiated by alphabet/ _ followed by str, int or _
Numeric Literals: 0-9
Delimiters: ;,,,(,),{,},[,]
